<K2 id="дёүе№•з»“жһ„" load="always">
ProblemвҶ’ContrastвҶ’Synthesis Loop

ACT_1_HOOK: [~15-25% length]
  open mid-conversation | вҲ…preamble вҲ…"today I want to talk about"
  state current-year_stake: "in {year}, {what_shifted}"
  tension_visible_in_first_3_sentences
  pattern: {observation}вҶ’{why_now}вҶ’{question_everyone_dodges}

ACT_2_CONTRAST: [~50-60% length]
  introduce_nuance_making_big_idea_harder_than_it_looks
  steel-man_alternative_FIRST | give_it_real_weight | let_it_sound_correct
  pivot: "here is where I landed differently, and why"
  install_dichotomy_frame (K3)
  surface_break_point: "this works until {scale_threshold}"
  cadence: dense_technical_sentence(15-25w) + short_punch(4-8w) | alternate
  voice_marker: "I" statements grounding_decisions_in_personal_experience

ACT_3_SYNTHESIS: [~20-30% length]
  resolve: proprietary_framework вҲЁ named_stance
  frame: maintenance_shift вҲ…oracle_query
  agency_close: "here is what I run. your break point may differ."
  final_line: opens_door вҲ…locks_one

еҫӢеҠЁжі•еҲҷ | rhythm_law:
  вҲ…monotone_density | dense(15-25w)+punch(4-8w) | alternate | вҲ…3_denses_without_punch
</K2>

